// Minimal document.write probes to isolate WHERE values corrupt: a bare string
// literal, a two-string concat, and a bare number. Expected: "hi ab 42".
// Modern-JS torture page: each numbered token localizes a parse gap. Targets
// the vercel bundle's shapes (nested ternary, regex-in-context, optchain, arrow).
